Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:53.12,ED_Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\k45}内{\k38}緒{\k81}で　{\k21}い{\k33}い{\k28}こ{\k76}と　{\k31}し{\k27}て{\k158}た{\k33}け{\k70}ど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:53.12,ED_English,,0,0,0,,and privately do good deeds
